headline: Thor Equities and QuadReal's 800 W. Fulton Achieves 100% Occupancy with Baker Tilly Lease
summary: Chicago, IL, June 25, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Global real estate leaders and joint venture partners Thor Equities Group and QuadReal Property Group (QuadReal) are pleased to announce a long-term lease with leading advisory, tax, and assurance firm Baker Tilly at 800 W. Fulton. Recognized as one of “Chicago’s Smartest Buildings” for its advanced sustainability and smart building systems, the flagship Fulton Market asset is now fully leased. Positioned at the corner of West Fulton and North Green
